nodes.text: Gungan fertility totems were Gungan artifacts used for fertility. They could be found in the Naboo system in the Chommell sector. During the Age of the Empire, Galactic Emperor Sheev Palpatine, a Naboo native, possessed a Gungan fertility totem and kept it on his personal yacht, the Imperialis. According to Sava Korin Pers, Gungan fertility totems were incredibly old, rare, and valuable.
